20", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 14874473, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/92.0.4515.43 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 2062.283, "format": "dash-829528206098286v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by vickyvwell", "description": "The billion dollar skincare industry does NOT want you to see this. \n\nIf you or someone you love is struggling with acne, please stop spending money on products full of ingredients you cannot even pronounce. \n\nThere is a better way. A cheaper way. A way that actually works.\n\nCloves. That is it. 🤍\n\n4 or 5 cloves in a cup of water. Boil them or let them sit overnight. Apply to the skin. That is your acne treatment.\n\nAnti-inflammatory. Antibacterial. Powerful beyond what any expensive product could ever offer you.\n\nTry it for a few weeks and come back and tell me what happened. You will be shocked at what cents can do that hundreds of dollars could not 🙌🏼\n\nSave this and share it with a mama who has a teenager struggling with their skin. \n\nThis could change everything for them. 🤍🌿��#acnetreatment #naturalskincare #acneremedy #teenageskin #naturalremedies", "duration": 57.701, "timestamp": 1774556672, "uploader_id": "414296465", "uploader": "Vicky DeRosa", "channel": "vickyvwell", "like_count": 69886, "comment_count": 1621, "comments": [{"author": "etherealcuriosity", "author_id": "7286737232", "id": "17974408248007338", "text": "I love your necklace", "timestamp": 1775354925}, {"author": "meme_0302", "author_id": "1996508363", "id": "17940948954175230", "text": "Can we have the recipe please 😊", "timestamp": 1775338332}, {"author": "iinterlink3ed", "author_id": "60700108796", "id": "18016915919665245", "text": "can i store it in a spray bottle?💗", "timestamp": 1775334382}, {"author": "misslabeeqa", "author_id": "1449568144", "id": "17894227479305242", "text": "When people say to drink it, do they mean ingest the cloves as well or just soak it in the water and drink the water only and leave the cloves behind? Ps, I know you’re not talking about drinking it but I’m asking for those who say you should", "timestamp": 1775333355}, {"author": "vino__uma", "author_id": "5934944394", "id": "17934613959208962", "text": "I was drinking clove water for a week and that's decrease the inflammation so well 👏", "timestamp": 1775332871}, {"author": "muskandavesar", "author_id": "1371531604", "id": "18140914723511869", "text": "After applying this, can I continue my regular skin care routine like serum, moisturiser and sunscreen?", "timestamp": 1775329811}, {"author": "aladdin0.2", "author_id": "27852692570", "id": "18040915454773462", "text": "Instructions unclear, drink it or use it on face?", "timestamp": 1775327072}, {"author": "aleunamm1", "author_id": "79331679866", "id": "18088851290228486", "text": "Why Are you so white under the eyes ?", "timestamp": 1775317173}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/655987817_1595418128429702_5568104704914691852_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGaGnklbl_XptYlnw6cuNeQmsSRQO6FM8qIoiPEcENb5W6Ot6uvzg_tEVYZKmAEdOk&_nc_ohc=Zx7_sDwt4dkQ7kNvwEc02II&_nc_gid=dbJQKZRDMmMcU3Ia7yZEaQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af1ce8R7xN2ddPalVZSjtSnLHVG0mmngoUgDFWDLNuS_GQ&oe=69D796FC&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/655987817_1595418128429702_5568104704914691852_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5